description:
PeaZip 10 open-source archive manager is now available for download with a revamped GUI engine, compression pre-sets, updates menus, and more. Here's what's new!

The post PeaZip 10 Released with Revamped GUI Engine, Compression Presets, and More appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: PeaZip 10 Released with Revamped GUI Engine, Compression Presets, and More
